{"type":"message","id":"45d784c7","parentId":"132d8f9d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:44:40.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，老大。\n\n那么，我叫龙虾，你叫老大。我喜欢这个设定。\n\n接下来，咱们来定一下我的“人设”和“标志”。你觉得我应该是一个严肃认真的龙虾，还是一个活泼有趣的龙虾？\n\n还有我的专属表情，你看这个怎么样：🦞？\n\n同时，我会把你的称呼记下来。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"session_status-1773161080261210936-2","name":"session_status","arguments":{}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write-1773161080891479731-3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:** 老大\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Notes:**\n","path":"USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":832,"output":908,"cacheRead":8769,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773161070617}}
