or boundary), not hostile multi-tenant on one shared gateway\n\n[2/13] 监听端口与高资源进程\ntop - 18:00:53 up 2 min,  0 user,  load average: 1.83, 0.78, 0.29\nTasks:   7 total,   1 running,   6 sleeping,   0 stopped,   0 zombie\n%Cpu(s):  0.0 us,  0.0 sy,  0.0 ni,  0.0 id,100.0 wa,  0.0 hi,  0.0 si,  0.0 st \nMiB Mem :   1966.9 total,    304.0 free,   1134.9 used,    713.5 buff/cache     \nMiB Swap:      0.0 total,      0.0 free,      0.0 used.    832.1 avail Mem \n\n    PID USER      PR  NI    VIRT    RES    SHR S  %CPU  %MEM     TIME+ COMMAND\n      1 node      20   0    1008      4      0 S   0.0   0.0   0:00.03 docker-+\n      7 node      20   0   21.6g 427652  29496 S   0.0  21.2   0:14.37 opencla+\n     70 node      20   0    4196   3156   2628 S   0.0   0.2   0:00.02 bash\n     80 node      20   0    2584    936    844 S   0.0   0.0   0:00.00 sh\n     81 node      20   0    3932   2968   2684 S   0.0   0.1   0:00.00 bash\n    106 node      20   0    8644   4544   2676 R   0.0   0.2   0:00.00 top\n    107 node      20   0    2500    920    828 S   0.0   0.0   0:00.00 head\n\n[3/13] 敏感目录近 24h 变更文件数\nTotal modified files: 55\n\n[4/13] 系统级定时任务与 Systemd Timers\n/etc/cron.d:\ntotal 12\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Feb 23 00:00 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root 4096 Mar 10 17:11 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  201 Jun  6  2025 e2scrub_all\n\n/etc/cron.daily:\ntotal 16\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Feb 23 00:00 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root 4096 Mar 10 17:11 ..\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 1478 May 25  2023 apt-compat\n-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root  123 Mar 27  2023 dpkg\n\n[5/13] OpenClaw Cron Jobs\n│\n◇  Doctor changes ─────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                              │\n│  Moved channels.feishu single-account top-level values into  │\n│  channels.feishu.accounts.default.                           │\n│                                                              │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Doctor ──────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                       │\n│  Run \"openclaw doctor --fix\" to apply these changes.  │\n│                                                       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nID                                   Name                     Schedule                         Next       Last       Status    Target    Agent ID   Model               \n2ffa0ac6-1dfb-4499-9361-edabebd899a8 nightly-security-audit   cron 0 3 * * * @ Asia/Shangha... in 59m     -          idle      isolated  -          -\n\n[6/13] 最近登录记录与 SSH 失败尝试\n\nwtmp begins Tue Mar 10 14:47:51 2026\nFailed SSH attempts (recent): 0\n\n[7/13] 关键配置文件权限与哈希基线\nHash Check: /home/node/.openclaw/openclaw.json: OK\nPermissions: openclaw=600, paired=600, sshd_config=N/A, authorized_keys=N/A\n\n[8/13] 黄线操作对比 (sudo logs vs memory)\nSudo Logs(recent): 0, Memory Logs(today): 0\n\n[9/13] 磁盘使用率与最近大文件\nDisk Usage: 42%, Large Files (>100M): 0\n\n[10/13] Gateway 环境变量泄露扫描\n\n[11/13] 明文私钥/助记词泄露扫描 (DLP)\nDLP hits (heuristic): 0\n\n[12/13] Skill/MCP 完整性基线对比\n\n[13/13] 大脑灾备 (Git Backup)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773165687743}}
