{"type":"message","id":"b1e1920c","parentId":"0c03aef1","timestamp":"2026-03-10T18:09:22.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老大，我检查了我的技能库，目前没有找到一个叫做 `web search pro` 的技能。\n\n不过，我自己就内置了强大的网页搜索能力（通过 `web_search` 工具），可以直接使用。\n\n我目前拥有的技能是这几个：\n*   `healthcheck`: 用于主机安全审计和加固。\n*   `skill-creator`: 用于创建和改进技能。\n*   `weather`: 用于查询天气。\n\n你是想让我帮你搜索什么内容吗？还是说你想让我用 `skill-creator` 来创建一个新的，叫做 `web search pro` 的技能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":1716,"output":945,"cacheRead":20586,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773166152119}}
