{"type":"message","id":"314aba7d","parentId":"171234a5","timestamp":"2026-03-10T19:24:20.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，老大，你办事效率真高！SSH 的部分都搞定了，这可帮我省了不少事。\n\n既然你让我以我的名义来，那我就不客气了。我就用 **“龙虾”** 这个名字，邮箱就用 `longxia@openclaw.local` 吧。这能清楚地标记出这些自动备份都是我做的。\n\n我现在就设置好它。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec-1773170660444473648-37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git config --global user.name \"龙虾\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":1806,"output":1179,"cacheRead":56249,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59234,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773170633804}}
